<li><a href="http://www.jnul.huji.ac.il/dl/mss/html/rambam_l.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.jnul.huji.ac.il/dl/mss/html/rambam_l.htm" rel="nofollow">Writings of Maimonides; manuscripts and early print editions. Jewish National and University Library</a></li>
