<p><i>This article incorporates text from the 1901–1906 <a href="/wiki/Jewish_Encyclopedia" title="Jewish Encyclopedia">Jewish Encyclopedia</a>&#160;article <a href="http://jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=905&amp;letter=M" class="external text" title="http://jewishencyclopedia.com/view.jsp?artid=905&amp;letter=M" rel="nofollow">"Moses Ben Maimon"</a>&#160;by <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Jacobs" title="Joseph Jacobs">Joseph Jacobs</a>, <a href="/wiki/Isaac_Broyd%C3%A9" title="Isaac Broydé">Isaac Broydé</a>, The Executive Committee of the Editorial Board, and <a href="/wiki/Jacob_Zallel_Lauterbach" title="Jacob Zallel Lauterbach">Jacob Zallel Lauterbach</a>, a publication now in the <a href="/wiki/Public_domain" title="Public domain">public domain</a>.</i></p>
